column4: I just fixed that exact same problem... I installed the deb manually with the --force-overwrite flag to dpkg.
how?
$ dpkg --force-overwrite python2.4 ?
and if you have a large error like that in the future, paste it into www.pastebin.com and post the link to it here please.
ok
that's it.
